Party Puffers, also known as party blowers or paper blow outs, are used at large celebrations
such as new years eve, or birthdays. The party puffer consists of a cylindrical mouth piece, which may or may
not be a whistle, attached to a coiled tube of paper.  When the mouth piece is blown into, the paper tube unravels and a
humorous festive noise is produced.